  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000219">
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[OnePetro] In a drillng context, a brake is the main device for stopping the travel of the drawworks of a rig when running or pulling a drill string.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[SLB Glossary] The mechanism on the drawworks that permits the driller to control the speed and motion of the drilling line and the drillstring.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[ISO 15926-4] A &lt;BRAKE&gt; is a &lt;FunctionalObject&gt; that has the capability of &lt;BRAKING&gt;</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[CFIHOS] A physical object intended to arrest or prevent the motion of an item. Typically by means of friction.</skos:definition>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">brake</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt-br">freio</rdfs:label>
    <iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom xml:lang="en">Every brake is an assembly that has the function of braking, and every assembly that has the function of braking is a brake.</iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="pt-br">Um freio é um conjunto que possui uma função de frenagem para deter ou prevenir o movimento de um objeto, tipicamente através da aplicação de força de atrito ou eletromagnética.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en">A brake is an assembly that bears a braking function to arrest or prevent the motion of an object, typically through friction or electromagnetic force application.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <owl:equivalentClass rdf:nodeID="nc1a1cc74203240db84b8ecd910de6f90b324"/>
    <skos:exactMatch rdf:resource="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000219"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom xml:lang="en">∀x(Brake(x) ↔ (Assembly(x) ∧ ∃f(BrakingFunction(f) ∧ bearerOf(x,f))))</iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="nc1a1cc74203240db84b8ecd910de6f90b194">
